Five members of one family were on Thursday night killed in a grisly road accident along the Nyeri Nyahururu highway. The family was coming from a function in Nyeri when the accident happened at Kianugu area. ALSO READ:

Woman killed by police car The personal car they were travelling in collided with a Nissan Matatu after their car got a tyre burst and rolled severally. Occupants in the personal car among them two children, a man and two women died on the spot. Other passengers were reffered to the Nyahururu County referral hospital with serious wounds. More to follow. 